data.description: Growing family? Need more space for toys and pets? This NFM 2 story home is perfect for you. Close to I75, under 16 minutes to both RSW and Punta Gorda airport and fast to downtown. Plenty of yard for a horse, chickens and all other fur babies. This home has had a total overhaul and lives like new with its LVP flooring, shaker cabinets with butcher block counters plus fresh paint and trim. 4 beds and 2 baths upstairs with a large bedroom and bathroom on the main level.Both levels of home are concrete and stucco, NEW AC, NEW Water Heater and ALL NEW Kitchen Appliances. The neatly manicured 1 acre property has so much wildlife to observe and enjoy. You must come see it to fully grasp what perfect country living can look like for you. Please take Elake Dr. instead of Tarpon, the paved road leads to this home with ease. See attached map picture for a guide.
